article_title: When model’s photo shoot gone wrong
article_text:
It was an embarrassing moment for the model who was trying to pose her best in a photo shoot but gone everything wrong hilariously when she fallen down to water.

Advertisement

The photo shoot of bikini model who was shooting at Malibu, California, ended up hilariously when a wave knocked the exercise ball and let the model into water.

According to the report, Bonnie Suarez, a Sports Fitness Magazine model, was told ‘look towards me’ by the director as she did the peculiar shoot, but she lost her balance as a wave came in and ended up on the sand.
